name: Balancer auraBAL Stable Pool
description: This token represents a Balancer Stable liquidity pool. Holders earn fees from users trading in the pools, and can also deposit the LP to Balancer's gauges to earn BAL emissions. This pool contains B-80BAL-20WETH and auraBAL. B-80BAL-20WETH is Balancer's governance token and auraBAL is Aura Finance's wrapped vote-escrowed B-80BAL-20WETH Balancer Pool Token.
